        "id": "emIRjfqC-ZDR"
      },
      "source": [
        "Workplace safety in hazardous environments like construction sites and industrial plants is crucial to prevent accidents and injuries. One of the most important safety measures is ensuring workers wear safety helmets.\n",
        "\n",
        "To overcome these challenges, SafeGuard Corp plans to develop an automated image analysis system capable of detecting whether workers are wearing safety helmets. This system will improve safety compliance and reduce workplace accidents."
      ]
